---Jetson commands ---

Create venv:
cd AgricultureBot
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

Create agbot (should only have to do once):
sudo nano /etc/systemd/system/agbot.service

---------
[Unit]
Description=Agriculture Bot FastAPI Server
After=network.target

[Service]
User=<YOUR_USERNAME>
WorkingDirectory=/home/<YOUR_USERNAME>/AgricultureBot

ExecStart=/bin/bash /home/<YOUR_USERNAME>/AgricultureBot/startup.sh

Restart=always
RestartSec=5

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target

-----------
sudo systemctl daemon-reload
sudo systemctl enable agbot
sudo systemctl start agbot
sudo systemctl status agbot
journalctl -u agbot -f


source ~/AgricultureBot/venv/bin/activate
uvicorn main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000

pip3 install pyserial
pip3 install inputs
pip3 install fastapi
pip3 install uvicorn
pip3 install websockets



install node js:
curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_20.x | sudo -E bash -
sudo apt-get install -y nodejs
npm install
--- In Interface ---
npm run dev -- --webpack

---For automatic hotspot:
1. Turn on automatic log in.
2. Go to startup applications
3. Add -> Call it auto hotspot -> give it the following command assuming the hotspot name is robot: nmcli connection up robot







